thread.title: BRIEF-Tianjin Motor Dies amends FY 2017 net profit outlook

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Tianjin Motor Dies amends FY 2017 net profit outlook

organizations.name: reuters) - tianjin motor dies co ltd

text:
Jan 31(Reuters) - Tianjin Motor Dies Co Ltd :
* Says net profit for FY 2017 to be 90 million yuan to 150 million yuan
* Says in the previous outlook, the company expected the net profit for FY 2017 to be 105 million yuan to 165 million yuan
* Says the net profit of FY 2016 was was 150 million yuan
Source text in Chinese: goo.gl/kmDxhN
